BOF expects a more detailed DMP according to the Flemish standard DMP template. You can find this template in DMPonline.be selecting that there is no funder associated with your project when creating the DMP, or you can use the word template provided by FWO

Please consult https://www.kuleuven.be/rdm/en/guidance/funder for more information about the funder requirements, and https://www.kuleuven.be/rdm/en/guidance/dmp/dmp for guidance on how to write a DMP
